name: As of 8/23
description:
As of 8/23 by Jarrett Cross | 2021 | VQGAN + CLIP, Photomanipulation, digital collage.

This is how my HEN art journal looks like from my iPad as of 8/23 of the year 2021. Marks a day of a personal milestone. 

I believe great things will happen.  

This piece is given to the collectors of my early works from my journal account.
